{
 "name": "RPlog_Jamon_s_Abduction",
 "title": "Jamon's Abduction",
 "summary": "In Caspar's SandBar, the Caspian pilot Jamon Grendine is charmed by a flirtatious Sarian woman, Breecia, who lures him out toward the beach and pulls a blaster on him in a dark alley. Drugged and locked in a makeshift cell, Jamon is interrogated by Breecia and her blond accomplice, who use a truth serum to extract a name from the resistant pilot while recording his testimony. The kidnappers, it emerges, are bargaining for the release of an imprisoned Twi'lek; Breecia mails Jamon's effects to his commander, the cold Shadow, demanding the trade. At an ebb-tide beach rendezvous, the two sides exchange the prisoner Kora for Jamon under leveled weapons, the tense swap going off without bloodshed before both parties race away into the night.",
